window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>“I didn’t plan to kill anyone. I wasn’t totally against the idea, either. Sometimes things just fall that way, and either you roll with it or it rolls over you. Letting the bad guys win isn’t how I roll.”</p> <p>Meet Joe Ledger, Baltimore PD, attached to a Homeland task force … who’s about to get a serious promotion.</p>"; 
